entries.complete: pcontrast1 CorSec Command: <pcontrast3  Good work, the REAL Cloak leader is destroyed. Return to the station for debriefing.pcontrast1  >
entries.title: Corellia System: Destroy the True Cloak Leader
entries.title_d: The ship that you captured was just a decoy! Since your auto-pilot override program is already wasted, you have no choice but to destroy the true Cloak leader.
